entropy.configuration

Interface ManagedElementSet<E extends ManagedElement>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>

    public interface ManagedElementSet<E extends ManagedElement>
extends List<E>
    Specify a list of managed elements without duplicated elements. The position of the element has to be maintained.
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
